"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector=self.webpackChunkwoocommerce_ebay_connector||[]).push([[620],{1822(e,a,t){e.exports=t.p+"assets/img/map-categories-tab.c344f877.webp"},50(e,a,t){t.r(a),t.d(a,{comp:()=>h,data:()=>l});var o=t(641);const i=t.p+"assets/img/manage-categories.93a2ac9a.webp",s=t.p+"assets/img/parent-category.486b75b1.webp";var r=t(1822);const n=t.p+"assets/img/sub-categories.b9238dfd.webp",c=t.p+"assets/img/condition.80d39c0e.webp",p=t.p+"assets/img/attribute.92161f12.webp",g=t.p+"assets/img/auto-mapping-setting.9331e37b.webp",m={},h=(0,t(6262).A)(m,[["render",function(e,a){return(0,o.uX)(),(0,o.CE)("div",null,[...a[0]||(a[0]=[(0,o.Fv)('<h1 id="category-mapping-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#category-mapping-–-woocommerce-ebay-connector"><span>Category Mapping – WooCommerce eBay Connector</span></a></h1><p>This section allows the admin to manage and map eBay categories with the WooCommerce store categories to ensure proper product organization.</p><hr><h2 id="managing-ebay-categories" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#managing-ebay-categories"><span>Managing eBay Categories</span></a></h2><p>The admin can import eBay categories so that the WooCommerce store automatically assigns imported products to the correct mapped categories.</p><ul><li>To view the list of imported categories, navigate to <strong>WC eBay Connector → Manage Categories</strong>.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/manage-categories.webp"><img src="'+i+'" alt="Manage Categories"></a></p><h3 id="how-to-import-ebay-categories" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#how-to-import-ebay-categories"><span>How to Import eBay Categories</span></a></h3><ul><li><strong>Create Primary Categories:</strong> Click the <strong>Create Primary Categories from eBay</strong> button to fetch the top-level categories.</li><li><strong>Import Node Categories:</strong> Click on <strong>Import all Node Category of this category</strong> to create the sub-categories within the WooCommerce store.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/parent-category.webp"><img src="'+s+'" alt="Import Parent Category"></a></p><hr><h2 id="mapping-ebay-categories-with-woocommerce" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#mapping-ebay-categories-with-woocommerce"><span>Mapping eBay Categories with WooCommerce</span></a></h2><p>After the categories are imported, the admin must map them to the corresponding WooCommerce store categories.</p><ul><li>Navigate to the <strong>Map Categories</strong> tab in the connector module.</li><li>This section provides the <strong>Map eBay Primary Categories</strong> option.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/map-categories-tab.webp"><img src="'+r+'" alt="Map Categories Tab"></a></p><h3 id="how-to-map-ebay-categories" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#how-to-map-ebay-categories"><span>How to Map eBay Categories</span></a></h3><ul><li>Click on <strong>Map eBay Primary Categories</strong> to start the mapping process.</li><li>Please note that the admin can map only <strong>one category</strong> at a time.</li><li>The mapping is applicable for <strong>sub-categories</strong> only; parent categories cannot be directly mapped.</li><li>Once mapped, the relationship between eBay and WooCommerce categories will appear in the list.</li></ul><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/sub-categories.webp"><img src="'+n+'" alt="Select Sub-Categories"></a></p><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/map-categories-tab.webp"><img src="'+r+'" alt="Mapped Category List"></a></p><blockquote><p>[!NOTE] During the mapping process, the admin can automatically create eBay conditions and specifications as WooCommerce product attributes.</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="ebay-category-conditions" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#ebay-category-conditions"><span>eBay Category Conditions</span></a></h2><p>Once a category is successfully mapped, the products within that category will display the <strong>eBay Category Condition</strong> field on the add/edit product page.</p><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/condition.webp"><img src="'+c+'" alt="Category Condition"></a></p><ul><li>The admin must provide the appropriate condition for each product to ensure successful export to eBay.</li><li>These conditions are fetched directly from the mapped eBay category.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="ebay-category-specifications" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#ebay-category-specifications"><span>eBay Category Specifications</span></a></h2><p>Mapped categories also enable <strong>eBay Category Specifications</strong>, which appear as global attributes in the product data section.</p><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/attribute.webp"><img src="'+p+'" alt="Product Attributes"></a></p><ul><li>The admin can view these specifications by navigating to <strong>Products → Attributes</strong> in the WordPress dashboard.</li><li>The system uses the mapped eBay category name to identify these global attributes.</li><li>Attributes follow the format: <strong>Attribute name [mapped category name]</strong>.</li><li>The admin must provide values for these mandatory attributes to comply with eBay listing requirements.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="automatic-category-mapping" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#automatic-category-mapping"><span>Automatic Category Mapping</span></a></h2><p>If the <strong>Auto Mapping</strong> feature is enabled, the connector will automatically assign imported eBay products to their respective pre-imported categories in WooCommerce.</p><p><a class="doc-image-link" href="./assets/auto-mapping-setting.webp"><img src="'+g+'" alt="Auto Mapping Setting"></a></p><h3 id="how-to-enable-auto-mapping" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#how-to-enable-auto-mapping"><span>How to Enable Auto Mapping</span></a></h3><ul><li>The admin navigates to <strong>WC eBay Connector → eBay Settings → General Settings</strong>.</li><li>Locate and toggle the <strong>Enable Auto Mapping</strong> option to <strong>Yes</strong>.</li><li>This automates the organization of incoming products from the eBay marketplace.</li></ul>',36)])])}]]),l=JSON.parse('{"path":"/documentation/category-mapping.html","title":"Category Mapping – WooCommerce eBay Connector","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{"prev":"/documentation/configuration.html","next":"/documentation/product-listing.html"},"git":{"contributors":[{"name":"shakir.hussain","username":"","email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","commits":1},{"name":"aadesh","username":"","email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","commits":3}],"changelog":[{"hash":"ba6d2edb5098181920dea430c0c44bcb4f5e451b","time":1774878680000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"update images"},{"hash":"2d5c39163a248635a79c60d8508c0716b0a11c03","time":1772114569000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"add export product"},{"hash":"a3379ad1acde7722f52940c853addb733657393e","time":1771942912000,"email":"aadesh.8209@webkul.in","author":"aadesh","message":"update images"},{"hash":"277c5a1bdc13e06551e102ee26c728b6b048e50b","time":1771481506000,"email":"shakir.hussain421@webkul.in","author":"shakir.hussain","message":"updated ebay blog and move to dev"}]},"filePathRelative":"documentation/category-mapping.md"}')}}]);